00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:25,020
Why did you

571
00:29:25,030 --> 00:29:26,170
reject Song Cong's offer?

572
00:29:26,180 --> 00:29:27,170
You had to force me

573
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:28,760
to use our parents' relationship, right?

574
00:29:30,580 --> 00:29:32,030
No.

575
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:34,110
Okay, we're all here.

576
00:29:34,580 --> 00:29:35,350
Let's go.

577
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,590
Where to?

578
00:29:36,700 --> 00:29:37,800
I'm taking you to experience

579
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,800
Chinese New Year
traditional preservation projects

580
00:29:39,800 --> 00:29:41,030
at our compound.

581
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:43,170
Let's go.

582
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,840
Why are you still sitting there?
Let's go.

583
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:45,660
You, too. Go.

584
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:47,020
Get up and walk around.

585
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:47,330
Where?

586
00:29:47,340 --> 00:29:48,300
You'll know soon.

587
00:29:48,310 --> 00:29:49,370
Where are you guys going?

588
00:29:49,380 --> 00:29:50,700
You'll know when we get there.

589
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,980
Mom, we're going out to play.

590
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:54,650
Be careful.

591
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:56,460
Mom, I'm leaving, too.

592
00:29:56,470 --> 00:29:57,170
Okay.

593
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:58,780
Follow them and stay safe.

594
00:29:58,790 --> 00:29:59,900
- Hope you win.
- Hold up.

595
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:00,540
Five characters.

596
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:01,610
Be careful on your way.

597
00:30:01,620 --> 00:30:03,110
I take it back.

598
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:06,020
No take-backs!

599
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:06,850
Go, quick.

600
00:30:06,860 --> 00:30:08,460
- Look.
- Nine circles.

601
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:09,350
Come.

602
00:30:21,310 --> 00:30:22,500
Nine circles.

603
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:23,890
Come on, I want it too.

604
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:25,180
Come on, two bamboos.

605
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:31,060
Is this the traditional project

606
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:32,420
you do every year?

607
00:30:32,950 --> 00:30:33,980
Where is Song?

608
00:30:33,990 --> 00:30:35,590
Come, log in.

609
00:30:50,790 --> 00:30:51,790
Jing Xichi.

610
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:53,830
What do I type in?

611
00:30:54,950 --> 00:30:56,070
Song, help her out.

612
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:00,110
Oh, I got it.

613
00:31:08,950 --> 00:31:11,070
What about the password?
What is the password?

614
00:31:11,470 --> 00:31:12,500
Zero, zero, zero. Here.

615
00:31:13,030 --> 00:31:13,700
Right.

616
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:44,830
Song.

617
00:31:45,100 --> 00:31:47,110
Why are you playing more and more
like a noob?

618
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:48,980
I'm taking a break.

619
00:31:49,020 --> 00:31:50,330
You should practice on your own.

620
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:51,740
Playing with you is a bore.

621
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:52,630
I'll play alone.

622
00:32:10,710 --> 00:32:12,980
(I feel like you've been
avoiding me recently.)

623
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:42,310
(What do you mean?)

624
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:49,850
(Since the final exams)

625
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:52,240
(until the end of the winter vacation,
I couldn't find you.)

626
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:08,270
(Tell me.)

627
00:33:08,310 --> 00:33:09,790
(What happened?)

628
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:29,870
(Although Qi Qi and I
still have some misunderstandings,)

629
00:33:30,140 --> 00:33:32,390
(she is still my best friend.)

630
00:33:32,620 --> 00:33:34,940
(I don't know what to do either.)

631
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:01,070
I'm too good.

632
00:34:01,750 --> 00:34:02,940
I'm too good.

633
00:34:02,950 --> 00:34:05,270
I'm really too good.

634
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,590
No one can beat me.

635
00:34:07,750 --> 00:34:08,940
Jing Xichi.

636
00:34:09,070 --> 00:34:10,420
Can we

637
00:34:10,470 --> 00:34:11,860
play something else?

638
00:34:11,870 --> 00:34:13,390
I don't know how to play games.

639
00:34:14,780 --> 00:34:15,980
Let's set off some fireworks.

640
00:34:16,470 --> 00:34:17,350
Sure.

641
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:20,150
Okay.

642
00:34:20,620 --> 00:34:21,860
But it's already so late.

643
00:34:21,870 --> 00:34:23,270
Where can we buy fireworks?

644
00:34:25,510 --> 00:34:26,420
I have an idea.

645
00:34:30,260 --> 00:34:33,100
This kid must be hiding himself.

646
00:34:47,550 --> 00:34:48,940
Such a big box.

647
00:34:49,140 --> 00:34:50,270
So much.

648
00:34:50,700 --> 00:34:52,100
Consider my debt paid.

649
00:34:52,830 --> 00:34:54,350
Where did you get it?

650
00:34:54,430 --> 00:34:55,390
From my dad's car.

651
00:34:55,950 --> 00:34:57,620
Impressive.

652
00:34:57,830 --> 00:34:58,420
Moreover,

653
00:34:58,430 --> 00:35:00,150
your family sets them off every year.

654
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:01,870
It's really noisy.

655
00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:04,100
Today, let's give the neighbors a break.

656
00:35:05,260 --> 00:35:07,230
Aren't you afraid of your dad...

657
00:35:07,470 --> 00:35:08,500
At worst, I'll get scolded

658
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,690
or beaten.

659
00:35:09,700 --> 00:35:11,310
He only had these two tricks.

660
00:35:16,350 --> 00:35:17,500
Leave quickly

661
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,790
before I change my mind.

662
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:22,460
You've stolen it anyway.

663
00:35:22,470 --> 00:35:23,420
Join us.

664
00:35:23,430 --> 00:35:24,190
Yes.

665
00:35:24,950 --> 00:35:25,980
Let's go together.

666
00:35:27,870 --> 00:35:30,460
I won't go. It's too noisy.

667
00:35:32,180 --> 00:35:33,710
Go quickly.

668
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:41,670
Thank you, brother.

669
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:43,100
Thanks.

670
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:47,830
Let's go set off some fireworks.

671
00:36:01,300 --> 00:36:02,420
Where can we set it off?

672
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:04,420
Over there.

673
00:36:06,070 --> 00:36:06,730
Let me tell you,

674
00:36:06,740 --> 00:36:08,060
these are the real deal.

675
00:36:08,070 --> 00:36:09,460
Stand far away.

676
00:36:10,550 --> 00:36:11,130
Xichi,

677
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:12,840
do you know
what this fireworks is called?

678
00:36:13,220 --> 00:36:15,020
Blue Dream.

679
00:36:15,550 --> 00:36:16,830
I will show you how dreamy it is.

680
00:36:27,620 --> 00:36:29,150
How long are

681
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:30,830
you guys going to avoid each other?

682
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:39,750
Did he tell you?

683
00:36:40,100 --> 00:36:42,230
Do you think he would tell me?

684
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:44,500
I could see it myself.

685
00:36:46,950 --> 00:36:48,310
He's not usually like this.

686
00:36:49,030 --> 00:36:50,540
Acting like he doesn't care.

687
00:37:01,470 --> 00:37:02,580
Chen Huan'er,

688
00:37:03,350 --> 00:37:04,980
I really know nothing

689
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:06,390
about girl stuff.

690
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:08,270
But I think

691
00:37:08,660 --> 00:37:11,310
friends are definitely pure-hearted.

692
00:37:11,740 --> 00:37:13,620
Just like I treat you as my friend.

693
00:37:14,030 --> 00:37:16,270
No matter what happens between us,

694
00:37:16,510 --> 00:37:18,020
I hope you are happy.

695
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:19,670
I hope you will prosper.

696
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:22,340
And I think

697
00:37:22,350 --> 00:37:24,100
you have done nothing wrong.

698
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:27,100
Don't be afraid of others' annoyance.

699
00:37:27,180 --> 00:37:28,940
Don't stop being yourself
because of that.

700
00:37:32,180 --> 00:37:33,310
Are you ready?

701
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,150
Ready.

702
00:37:35,260 --> 00:37:36,190
Here we go.

703
00:37:58,950 --> 00:38:00,420
There is a bigger one over there.

704
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:06,850
♪You can pretend it's okay♪

705
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:09,860
♪Where are your thoughts?♪

706
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:13,420
♪Does he understand?♪

707
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:15,830
Chen Huan'er,

708
00:38:17,180 --> 00:38:20,190
we all have a pure
revolutionary camaraderie.

709
00:38:20,470 --> 00:38:22,790
You must not let us down.

710
00:38:25,870 --> 00:38:27,670
That's right.

711
00:38:27,830 --> 00:38:30,580
Don't destroy the harmony
in our organization!

712
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:33,420
We are becoming juniors.

713
00:38:33,430 --> 00:38:37,150
We need to study hard.

714
00:38:39,580 --> 00:38:43,420
♪That's not real me♪

715
00:38:45,430 --> 00:38:48,190
I see!

716
00:38:48,620 --> 00:38:52,010
♪Don't let tears fall♪

717
00:38:52,020 --> 00:38:55,020
♪I get the answer I'm waiting for♪

718
00:38:55,030 --> 00:38:59,050
♪Did anyone really hear it?♪

719
00:38:59,060 --> 00:39:01,010
♪Say the perfect lie♪

720
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:04,820
♪Become the one who
understands you the best♪

721
00:39:04,900 --> 00:39:08,610
♪Stay as friends, even as a pretense♪

722
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:12,780
♪As long as I am♪

723
00:39:15,740 --> 00:39:17,700
♪missed by you♪

724
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:32,020
Where did you put the fireworks?

725
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:34,100
In the trunk?

726
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:35,860
I've checked it. It's not there.

727
00:39:35,870 --> 00:39:37,100
Please help me find it.

728
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:40,940
How can they fail such a simple task?

729
00:39:43,390 --> 00:39:44,460
Have you seen

730
00:39:44,470 --> 00:39:45,520
the fireworks in my trunk?

731
00:39:46,830 --> 00:39:48,150
I didn't see it.

732
00:39:48,180 --> 00:39:50,580
Why didn't you see if it's in the trunk?

733
00:39:51,700 --> 00:39:53,210
How would I see it?

734
00:39:53,220 --> 00:39:54,460
Are you serious?

735
00:39:54,550 --> 00:39:56,250
The fireworks in your trunk.

736
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:57,540
I'm not in your trunk.

737
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:59,060
You can check it out yourself!

738
00:39:59,070 --> 00:39:59,770
Why ask me?

739
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:00,690
I was watching TV here

740
00:40:00,700 --> 00:40:01,940
peacefully.

741
00:40:01,950 --> 00:40:04,290
Why are you watching TV?

742
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:05,860
You don't care about our son!

743
00:40:05,870 --> 00:40:08,060
Seriously, you are weird.

744
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:08,860
Why are you upset?

745
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:09,980
You talk too much.

746
00:40:09,990 --> 00:40:11,860
Why are you throwing a tantrum at me?

747
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:12,690
Tone it down!

748
00:40:12,700 --> 00:40:13,900
You take care of him usually.

749
00:40:13,910 --> 00:40:14,850
Oh, really?

750
00:40:14,850 --> 00:40:16,780
But you throw a tantrum
right when you come home!

751
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,060
Tell me, is that right?

752
00:40:18,180 --> 00:40:19,020
Tell me.

753
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:20,460
Just help me to look for it, okay?

754
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:21,610
Go look for it yourself.

755
00:40:21,620 --> 00:40:22,620
I'm not messing with you.

756
00:40:22,660 --> 00:40:24,230
How dare you ask me to look for it!

757
00:40:42,830 --> 00:40:44,380
Huan'er, over here.

758
00:40:44,390 --> 00:40:46,180
Anything you want to say
to your future self?

759
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,250
Stop recording.

760
00:40:47,260 --> 00:40:48,500
Just say a few words, come on.

761
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:50,230
Song is here. Record him.

762
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:51,100
Song.

763
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:53,420
Oh, you are still hooked on that?

764
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:55,170
This has eight megapixels.

765
00:40:55,180 --> 00:40:56,020
You know?

766
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:56,580
Say something.

767
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,650
Stop lying.

768
00:40:57,660 --> 00:40:58,820
I checked it out yesterday.

769
00:40:58,830 --> 00:40:59,980
It's just three megapixels.

770
00:41:01,260 --> 00:41:02,570
Who cares?

771
00:41:02,580 --> 00:41:03,650
It works, doesn't it?

772
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:05,100
I can say whatever I want.

773
00:41:09,430 --> 00:41:10,340
Li Tian.

774
00:41:10,350 --> 00:41:11,120
Come, say something.

775
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:12,940
Anything you want to say
to your future self?

776
00:41:12,940 --> 00:41:14,340
Why are you running? Li Tian.

777
00:41:14,350 --> 00:41:15,500
Li Tian, hold up.

778
00:41:19,910 --> 00:41:20,860
It's useless to run.

779
00:41:20,870 --> 00:41:22,500
I will definitely catch you on camera.

780
00:41:22,830 --> 00:41:25,500
No one can escape me.

781
00:41:43,521 --> 00:41:48,691
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

782
00:41:50,481 --> 00:41:55,561
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

783
00:41:57,331 --> 00:42:02,681
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

784
00:42:02,991 --> 00:42:08,481
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

785
00:42:11,071 --> 00:42:16,091
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

786
00:42:17,881 --> 00:42:23,121
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

787
00:42:24,721 --> 00:42:30,141
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

788
00:42:30,601 --> 00:42:36,101
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

789
00:42:37,301 --> 00:42:41,261
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

790
00:42:41,261 --> 00:42:46,251
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

791
00:42:46,381 --> 00:42:49,811
♪And full of life♪

792
00:42:51,101 --> 00:42:54,561
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

793
00:42:54,561 --> 00:42:59,671
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

794
00:42:59,931 --> 00:43:04,321
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

795
00:43:04,821 --> 00:43:08,721
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

796
00:43:08,721 --> 00:43:13,661
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

797
00:43:13,661 --> 00:43:16,451
♪To know right from wrong♪

798
00:43:18,361 --> 00:43:21,891
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

799
00:43:21,891 --> 00:43:25,141
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

800
00:43:25,301 --> 00:43:31,061
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

801
00:43:31,481 --> 00:43:36,081
♪At just the right time♪
